{"tid":2496807,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[上市公司] 譚仔阿姐仲高人工過FG","createTime":"2021-04-20T05:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T05:47:12.000Z","uid":43261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a57e890bdb04a3449d4ec0d23dd014cdb6232461","tid":2496807,"uid":43261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQH9djfEkC4byAWoNJHqHaigRPrp6v5Mqq7a5CiHUPCC3?filename=U8zFVbP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8zFVbP.jpg&h=c85539b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經營「譚仔雲南米線」及「譚仔三哥米線」品牌的譚仔國際日前向港交所遞交上市申請，公司亦公佈了整個成本結構，當中員工成本為4億元，佔總收入的28％。那麼即將成為上市公司員工的「譚仔姐姐」目前的人工又有幾多？<br />\n<br />\n據招聘網站Jooble，譚仔在本月的招聘日以每月薪金16,500元至20,000元招聘「侍應／廚房助理／洗碗」，尚未計及新人獎金、勤工獎、醫療和交通津貼；而譚仔三哥則以最高薪金17,000元招侍應。若按中位數計，譚仔姐姐的月入中位數達18,200元。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessdigest.io/data/行業數據-譚仔國際即將上市-譚仔姐姐人工又有幾多\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessdigest.io%2Fdata%2F%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E8%AD%9A%E4%BB%94%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-%E8%AD%9A%E4%BB%94%E5%A7%90%E5%A7%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%88%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E5%A4%9A&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuBqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=3361ca21\" target=\"_blank\">https://businessdigest.io/data/行業數據-譚仔國際即將上市-譚仔姐姐人工又有幾多</a>"},{"pid":"dc691d7965f2f369f252ab8b768ceb83c179cd7d","tid":2496807,"uid":30246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"入職條件：<br />\n操流利譚仔話，勤力，需體力勞動；工作範圍包括但不限於樓面工作、洗碗、收銀、環境清潔；有經驗者優先"},{"pid":"eea4e8cba3b61e79628d331f62017a171cf810b4","tid":2496807,"uid":358058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"都話政府比狗做，譚仔阿姐人工仲高過aco/ca師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918b19238b82c16eb140f001c99a32ba14ad4bf7","tid":2496807,"uid":26766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eea4e8cba3b61e79628d331